snippet.title: Brooke Vs. World Doom - Winter Assault Gameplay Trailer - SAGE Expo 2022
snippet.description:
An all new playable for Brooke Vs. World Doom includes fan-favorite snowy level Winter Assault, a heart pounding thrill-ride through the mysterious mountains! Symmetrico's hiding away a secret base deep within old castle ruins, forgotten by time, and it's up to you to rip through their defensive to break in, using any means necessary.

You can play the first three levels today, all included in the official Steam demo! Visit the game's online booth at SAGE Expo 2022 to get started!
https://www.sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/brooke-vs-world-doom.1350/

Get weekly progress updates on Brooke:
https://twitter.com/SlyBalto
